chive.org/web/20070612051615/http://www.h-net.org/reviews/showrev.cgi?path=252691081495762 |date=12 June 2007 }} H-Net Review: John Radzilowski</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"jcpa.org\">[http://www.jcpa.org/cjc/cjc-schudrich-06.htm The Chief Rabbi's View on Jews and Poland \u2013 Michael Schudrich]. Jcpa.org. Retrieved on 22 August 2010.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"jewishvirtuallibrary.org\">[https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/vjw/Warsaw.html The Virtual Jewish History Tour \u2013 Warsaw]. Jewishvirtuallibrary.org. Retrieved on 22 August 2010.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"lukas\">Richard Lukas ''Forgotten Holocaust'', Hippocrene Books, 2nd revised ed., 2001, {{ISBN|0-7818-0901-0}}.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"opoczno-1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.opoczno.pl/opoczno/_portal/117189707245d9baf044536/Zabytki.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205110952/http://www.opoczno.pl/opoczno/_portal/117189707245d9baf044536/Zabytki.html|url-status=dead|title=Official portal of the city of Opoczno|archivedate=5 December 2008}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"partners-1\">[http://www.friends-partners.org/partners/beyond-the-pale/index.html Beyond the Pale] Online exposition</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"polish-jewish-heritage.org\">[http://www.polish-jewish-heritage.org/eng/05-01_Polan_Selects_New_Chief_Rabbi.htm The Canadian Foundation of Polish-Jewish Heritage]. Polish-jewish-heritage.org (8 January 2005). Retrieved on 2010-08-22.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"relations\">[https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/vjw/Poland.html The Virtual Jewish History Tour \u2013 Poland]. Jewishvirtuallibrary.org. Retrieved on 22 August 2010.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"response\">[http://www.fathom.com/course/72809602/session3.html Poland's Century: War, Communism and Anti-Semitism] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307025436/http://www.fathom.com/course/72809602/session3.html |date=7 March 2009 }}. Fathom.com. Retrieved on 22 August 2010.</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"stroop\">From the [https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/